ion.setNeedsUpdateSize() \/\/ Updates the annotation size."]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" uses "},{"code":"UIView.systemLayoutSizeFitting(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to measure the view size. Make sure that your view returns the correct size (e.g. implemented using AutoLayout, or returns correct size from "},{"code":"UIView.sizeThatFits(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when layout is manual)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To remove annotation when it’s no longer needed, use ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotation\/remove()"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"View Annotations","generated":true,"anchor":"View-Annotations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationManager","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationOptions","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationManagerError","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationAnchorConfig","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationPositionDescriptor","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationUpdateObserver","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotationAnchor"]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotation\/init(annotatedFeature:view:)","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotation\/init(coordinate:view:)","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/ViewAnnotation\/init(layerId:featureId:view:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","gene